{
  "name": "Ingest Health - Baseline Builder",
  "description": "Daily per-device baseline rebuild over 168h. Each savelookup LRQ uses a POLL LOOP: launch -> capture id+forward-tag -> loop {poll(GET) -> if stepsCompleted = totalSteps break, else delay 5s and retry (cap 60)} -> next. Writes ingestHealthBaseline and ingestHealthSourceStats. Bind 'SentinelOne SDL' (Bearer) on all http_request actions.",
